Serves 4 – 6 You’ll need: 150g McCain Potato Crispers; 100g salami; 100g mozzarella cheese; 60g black olives For the tomato sauce – 30ml olive oil; 1 onion, peeled and roughly chopped; 2 garlic cloves, finely chopped; ½ celery stalk, roughly chopped; 800g tinned whole peeled tomatoes; 40g tomato paste; 5ml honey; fresh basil, to serve How to: Enjoy scooping with family and friends! *Recipe and image by McCain.